{"tid":1757934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同時間有兩條女追我 想問點揀好？","createTime":"2019-11-26T19:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T06:53:23.000Z","uid":325757,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"22342fb15cf347763b365e0e98fb57686be9c6b0","tid":1757934,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:03:26.000Z","msg":"兩個都係姐姐樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個矮過我 細細粒粒咁 瘦底 幾可愛 個樣都靚嘅 性格好活潑多嘢講 好善談 同佢一齊相處係幾開心 不過份人感覺有啲單純容易呃 怕容易戴帽 <br />\n<br />\n另外一個就高過我 瘦底 樣成熟 姐姐feel 完全係我杯茶 可惜就係高過我 不過我都唔係咁介意其實 性格就比上面嗰個文靜同奇怪 斯文類型 唔多嘢講嘅 同佢相處有種細水長流嘅感覺 係溫馨同幸福嘅感覺 無乜缺點 係份人比較難捉摸 成日自相矛盾 做啲嘢似係又唔似係咁 不過佢做啲嘢似似地收兵🤔但係佢性格又唔多似<br />\n<br />\n好煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人試過？想問下揀邊個會好啲？<br />\n<br />\n利申 兩個都唔鍾意 所以兩個都唔會揀"},{"pid":"05743843ca3e6a6d0f3969b77c3131d67be85d52","tid":1757934,"uid":44516,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"自己都有答案 開po把撚"},{"pid":"1420bee36ae4059bb94f11e5e368c524cd89eb0d","tid":1757934,"uid":228436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意咁揀乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0754c118cb7dd16e64454f3dc25377f8e878f9","tid":1757934,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1420bee36ae4059bb94f11e5e368c524cd89eb0d","tid":1757934,"uid":228436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意咁揀乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:06:55.000Z","msg":"我都無話揀嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752a0c78321c6712626fc4ae11db7d95d0fcc215","tid":1757934,"uid":136457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:07:20.000Z","msg":"想屌閪姐 一個輪住一個咪得"},{